## 🔧 Quick Reference

### Creating New Components on either "mobile" or "web" packages

1. Determine correct FSD layer (entity/feature/widget/shared)
2. Create appropriate segment (ui/model/api/lib)
3. Export through `index.ts` barrel file
4. Follow naming conventions (PascalCase for components)

### Styling Components for "web" package

1. Use Tailwind CSS classes
2. Apply `cn()` utility for conditional classes
3. Use custom CSS variables for theming
4. Follow responsive design patterns

This project represents a modern, scalable frontend monorepo architecture for mobile and web platforms with clean code practices.
